The "PatientCare Pro" app respects and protects the privacy of all users who use the service. In order to provide you with more accurate and more personalized services, the "PatientCare Pro" app will use and disclose your personal information in accordance with the provisions of this privacy policy. However, the "PatientCare Pro" app will treat this information with a high level of diligence and prudence. Except as otherwise provided in this Privacy Policy, the “Fuel consumption statistics” app will not disclose this information to external parties or provide it to third parties without your prior permission. The "PatientCare Pro" app will update this Privacy Policy from time to time. When you agree to the "PatientCare Pro" app service use agreement, you are deemed to have agreed to the full content of this Privacy Policy. This Privacy Policy is an integral part of the "PatientCare Pro" app service usage agreement.

1. Scope of application

  (a) User's personal data obtained by a "PatientCare Pro" app from a business partner through legal means.

2. Use of information

